中班的小朋友(开始认识字，特别爱打破沙锅问到底)<br>\nA: 这位是que叔叔……<br>\n中班小朋友贝贝： que叔叔？ 是麻雀的雀吗？<br>\n阙叔叔:啊哈哈……<br>\n……<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n</p>","fields":{"slug":"/2018-10-31/how-to-introduce-yourself/","prefix":"2018-10-31"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to introduce yourself ?","author":"文:Jane 图(泡泡射手):贝贝","category":"funny","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/cc95fa7f9ee773beb37de90322313764/ada8c/bubble_shooter.jpg"}}}}},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-11-02/sincerity/","prefix":"2018-11-02"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The essence of communication —— sincerity?"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-10-30/meditation/","prefix":"2018-10-30"},"frontmatter":{"title":"瑜伽冥想引导词"}},"authornote":{"id":"9fe62122-025b-556e-8f79-c5d93f344df9","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2018-10-31/how-to-introduce-yourself/","total":38,"prev":"/2018-11-02/sincerity/","next":"/2018-10-30/meditation/"}}